{"type": "article", "id": 25671, "title": "如何制造充满魔力的现场？米兰设计周这几场展值得借鉴", "description": "想要打造魔力感，一定要玩好光和影。这里有三个来自日本设计师的例子。", "date": "2016-04-19T14:26:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22719, "name": "室内装置"}, {"id": 26427, "name": "光影"}, {"id": 9003, "name": "米兰设计周"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 26428, "name": "Asahi Glass"}, {"id": 26429, "name": "Nosigner"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 155, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607120707aTPrt8yDhpCdN0cI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>大概在两个月前，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/22711.html\">我们曾在一篇文章中介绍过</a>，<a href=\"http://www.sou-fujimoto.net\">日本建筑师藤本壮介（Sou Fujimoto）</a>将和 COS 在米兰设计周上合作，打造一片“光之森林”。从当时公布的概念图可以看出，一束束聚光灯被高高悬挂在天花板上，投射下来的光线构成了一片光海。4 月 17 号，在米兰设计周的 <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Arti/@45.4660772,9.2021514,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x3981229bfb8e46cb\">Cinema Arti</a>，人们终于看到了这片灯光森林的真面目，<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/04/12/sou-fujimoto-cos-forest-of-light/\">模特们在灯光下行走，充满了艺术感</a>。</p>\n<p>COS 的总经理 Marie Honda 曾在接受 Dezeen 采访时表示，“建筑和设计对于 COS 来说有着至关重要的影响。”这或许是 COS 选择与建筑师合作的原因。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120656gdjsEGhiUm6Ma5OT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> 米兰设计周 COS × \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSou Fujimoto 装置现场 </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120657RLS1UuaE08oFdhmw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4986376\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">多个灯光倾泻而下，颇为壮观</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071206578HVA1jd9iLucSprk.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66517857\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120659BTDmnOaLPg09f83p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120659hWOXVGFCz5Te4gai.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">展览现场，人与空间形成了互动关系</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>除了藤本壮介 ，另一位日本设计师也在米兰设计周打造了充满魔性的空间。</p>\n<p>这是一个叫作 “<a href=\"http://www.agc-milan.com/mdw/2016/?lang=en\">Amorphous</a>” 的展览，是设计事务所 Nosigner 和<a href=\"http://www.asahi-glass.com/cn/index.html\">日本玻璃制造商 Asahi Glass </a>共同创作的装置。</p>\n<p>在多彩的灯光下，<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/04/14/the-molecular-structure-of-glass-magnified-and-recreated-with-5000-pieces-of-glass/\">5000 多块玻璃闪烁着耀眼的光泽</a>——玻璃是一种常见的材料，我们每天都会见到，但在这个空间里，人们能充分领略到它们呈现出的多样性和复杂性。玻璃每个角度都有着不同的色调，十分炫目耀眼，形成了一个充满魔力的空间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120659VJWEyQmuog4r5ePf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120700mSwf9Ft1Hr4uj3TL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4986376\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071207019Apr86VeC5Y1hEqB.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712070156y90tMJvBp2fwCN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56026786\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120703yOWeGfcbYzaBEHn8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">上面两个案例说明了灯光的重要性。灯光能被运用在大型空间，还能被运用在小巧思上。</p>\n<p class=\"\">本次米兰时装周上，<a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/about/\">日本设计事务所 YOY</a> 设计了一个名叫 “Depth” 的装置，他们在一副平面作品背后加了 LED 灯光，给平面图像塑造了光影深度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120704dwzpqmSOFMA1tkJN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56026786\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120705apY8bJzjqfyteHcB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66336634\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">平面的图画呈现出了立体的光影</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/about/\">YOY 设计事务所</a>由两位年轻的设计师组成，他们分别是空间设计师 Naoki Ono 和产品设计师 Yuki Yamamoto 。该工作室成立于 2011 年，他们二人构思奇特，充分利用光和影在营造氛围。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120705ZceIT28Cdn0DBzVp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">这是一个墙灯，像是剥离的墙纸</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120705UvXD4QZsG8ymLqCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.48663102\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">落地灯</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607120706KfzAt7uagXiH1k32.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40318302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071207069dvXRsCabKYFw26M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一张纸做成的灯</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2016/04/12/sou-fujimoto-cos-forest-of-light/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">spoon-tamago</a><br></p>\n\n\n\n"}